<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.2">
<l>kaṇṇuḷ ḷēniṟkuṅ kātaṉmai yāṟoḻi</l>
<l>leṇṇi lumvaru meṉṉiṉi vēṇṭuva</l>
<l>maṇṇu nīru meriyunal vāyuvum</l>
<l>viṇṇu māyviri yumempi rāṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He stands in [my] eye. Even if I count the services</l>
<l>[accomplished] through loving, what will come now? We want</l>
<l>our lord who expands as earth, water</l>
<l>fire, good winds and sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
